{"tid":1687471,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"證券藍list更新 1","createTime":"2019-11-02T00:54:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T15:42:29.000Z","uid":325838,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"40181c86057aa9b4ac94a743eee779536a4a9ffb","tid":1687471,"uid":325838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T00:54:38.000Z","msg":"證券藍list更新 1<br />\n<br />\n鑑於渣打員工涉嫌泄漏黃絲客戶私隱資料, 大家要對於需要提供地址電話等個人資料獲得服務的公司格外小心, 假如該公司管理層是藍絲, 絕對有可能濫權指示下屬作出類似渣打員工的行為<br />\n<br />\n證券藍list<br />\n<br />\n藍絲證券行<br />\n- 中原證券 (施永青旗下)<br />\n<br />\n中資證券行<br />\n- 富途<br />\n- 華盛<br />\n- 友信<br />\n<br />\n較可靠證券行<br />\n- 致富 (肯光明正大澄清立場)<br />\n- 輝立 (新加坡資本)<br />\n- interative brokers (美國資本)<br />\n- Fundsupermart (FSM) (新加坡資本)<br />\n<br />\n呢個list可隨時更新, 包括修改和新增, 請各位手足幫忙提供更多資料<br />\n<br />\n另外, 如果你發覺有證券行有泄漏你個人資料的嫌疑, 請保留証據及向證監會作出強硬投訴"},{"pid":"593dcc9ac85456c457f80238d5a34546af6cf114","tid":1687471,"uid":325838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T00:55:22.000Z","msg":"原po<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1678206\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1678206</a>"},{"pid":"4f5435f030206371ff361f93e0907cb586a536b4","tid":1687471,"uid":325838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T00:55:45.000Z","msg":"有無手足幫手fc 下韓寶生有無被人炒?"},{"pid":"bff88aa40a8a0b1fe7f5ea2c6480f5c3fa590649","tid":1687471,"uid":285261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T00:55:46.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n好重要<br />\n各行各業都要有"},{"pid":"cf3fdd933a783d334fe4d16e6b3e7395013bd5ff","tid":1687471,"uid":255980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T00:59:44.000Z","msg":"一通呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a7dde9b3ce755fe39d69a56985b49d5135150ab","tid":1687471,"uid":325838,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cf3fdd933a783d334fe